		VMM (Vreng Machine Monitoring)


General stuffs
--------------

For compiling classes, type:

	# ./configure
	# make

For installing, type:

	# make install

Thek edit the file vmm.conf to adapt it to your system.

For using collector, type:

	# vmm

For some help, type:

	# vmm --help

Warning: don't use option '--preferences' because it's already used
         in script 'vmm'.
         If you want to specify an other path for preferences file,
         edit 'vmm' script.


The preferences file : vmm.conf
-------------------------------

Index of color:
  0  : black
  1  : blue
  2  : cyan
  3  : darkGray
  4  : gray
  5  : green
  6  : lightGray
  7  : magenta
  8  : orange
  9  : pink
  10 : red
  11 : white
  12 : yellow

Description of fields in file 'collector.ini'

Networking properties.
  domain_name			: Domaine name.
  subnet_mask			: Netmask.
  generic_multicast_adress	: Generic IP address for multicast.
  multicast_port		: Port for multicast addresses.
  multicast_TTL			: TTL for multicast addresses.
  vreng_root_URL		: Root URL for accessing to vreng homepage.

IO properties.
  stats_path			: Root path for 'vmm'.
  vmm_directory			: 'vmm' directory.
  vre_directory			: Directory where there is 'vre' source file.
  vre_extension			: 'vre' file extension.
  world_filename		: File name of serialized object 'World'.
  collecting_filename		: File name of infos in text.


Servers which collector must represent.
  servers			: Present servers on machine.

Default entry position in a place.
  entry_x			: Default entry position in a place : x coord.
  entry_y			: Default entry position in a place : y coord.
  entry_z			: Default entry position in a place : z coord.
  entry_radius			: Default entry position in a place : angle coord.

Main aspect of a subnetwork place.
  subnet_sky_color              : Color of background in a subnetwork.
  subnet_default_width		: Default dimension of a subnet (in meters) : width.
  subnet_default_length		: Default dimension of a subnet (in meters) : lenght.
  subnet_floor_texture_URL	: Used texture for subnetwork floor.
  subnet_wall_texture_URL	: Used texture for subnetwork wall.
  room_door_spacing		: Space between two doors in a subnetwork representation.

Main aspect of a room place.
  room_sky_color                : Color of background in a room.
  room_default_width		: Default dimension of a room (in meters) : width.
  room_default_length		: Default dimension of a room (in meters) : height.
  room_floor_texture_URL	: Used texture for room floor.
  room_wall_texture_URL		: Used texture for room wall.

Main aspect of a machine place.
  machine_sky_color             : Color of background in a machine.
  machine_default_width		: Default dimension of a machine (in meters) : width.
  machine_default_length	: Default dimension of a machine (in meters) : height.
  machine_floor_texture_URL	: Used texture for machine floor.
  machine_wall_texture_URL	: Used texture for machine wall.

Parameters for a machine in a room or a subnetwork.
  machine_spacing		: Space between two machines (in meter) in a subnetwork or a room reprentation.
  machine_width			: 3D dimension of machine : width.
  machine_height		: 3D dimension of machine : height.
  machine_depth			: 3D dimension of machine : depth.
  machine_texture_URL		: Used texture to map one face of a machine

Dimension of walls.
  wall_height			: Height for a wall.
  wall_depth			: Depth for a wall.

Representation of a panel.
  panel_width			: Panel dimension : width.
  panel_height			: Panel dimension : height.
  panel_depth			: Panel dimension : depth.
  panel_tee_width		: Width of tee for a panel.
  panel_text_height		: Height for text on a panel.
  panel_texture_URL		: Texture for a panel.
  panel_font_URL		: Font used to write on a panel.

Representation of a door.
  door_width			: Door dimension : width.
  door_height			: Door dimension : height.
  door_depth			: Door dimension : depth.
  door_texture_URL		: Texture for a door.

Spacing between two elements in a machine representation.
  features_spacing		: Spacing between different feature in a machine.

Representation of users.
  user_spacing			: Spacing between two users.
  user_head_radius		: Radius of head for user representation.
  user_head_color		: Color of head.
  user_tee_radius		: Radius of tee cylinder of user representation.
  user_tee_height		: Its height.
  user_tee_color		: Color of tee.

Representation of a day for uptime.
  day_spacing			: Spacing between two day representations.
  day_radius			: Radius of sphere for day representation.
  day_color			: Color for a day representation.

Representation of load.
  mean_load_radius		: Dimension of cylinder for mean representation : radius.
  mean_load_height		: Dimension of cylinder for mean representation : height.
  mean_load_color		: Color for mean load representation.

Representation of swap.
  swap_radius			: Dimension of cylinder for swap representation : radius.
  swap_height			: Dimension of cylinder for swap representation : height.
  swap_color			: Color for free space of swap.

Representation of a process.
  process_spacing		: Spacing between two process representations.
  process_width			: Dimension of each process representation : width.
  process_height		: Dimension of each process representation : height.
  process_depth			: Dimension of each process representation : depth.
  process_color			: Color for each process representation.

Representation of servers.
  server_spacing		: Spacing between two server representations.
  server_radius			: Server dimension : radius of base.
  server_height			: Server dimension : height.
  server_color			: Color for a server representation.

Representation of space disk.
  space_spacing			: Spacing between two spacse representation.
  space_radius			: Dimension of space cylinder : radius.
  space_height			: Dimension of space cylinder : height.
  space_color			: Color of free space.
